{"tid":86767,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"違反紅十字會規則！電子遊戲不容許用「紅色十字」符號","createTime":"2017-01-19T10:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T04:54:13.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c595faebd6ff601a7b70a53d3924d67389c9a6e2","tid":86767,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:09:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/01/17/red-cross-symbol-in-games/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F01%2F17%2Fred-cross-symbol-in-games%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=USo9LOJMBp8EuMlQhn0d76EBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=031769b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/01/17/red-cross-symbol-in-games/game-channel/</a> <br />\n<br />\n若然大家在遊戲中看到「紅色十字」，相信絕大部份人應該會即是想到急救、治療或補血之類的含意。不過這個標誌性符號以後或未必能再在遊戲中出現，皆因最近《Prison Architect》遊戲開發商 Introversion 收到英國紅十字會通知，並表示遊戲中採用紅色十字符號並不合法。 <br />\n<br />\nSource:<img src=\"https://css.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/001-89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcss.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F001-89.jpg&h=32a14828&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n違反紅十字會規則！電子遊戲不容許用「紅色十字」符號去代表急救 <br />\n<br />\n紅色十字在遊戲界中已存在一段時間，不過據 PC Gamer 報導原來這個符號並非在公眾領域，反而是由國際紅十字會監管，而今次他們的行動似乎是希望保護符號不被濫用。紅十字會向 Introversion 發出的通知則指出，紅十字符號或類似的標誌若用於其他目的，即使它們如何有益處或無關痛癢，但始終都會影響到標誌本身的特殊意義。紅十字同時亦強調這個標誌並不代表救護車、保健、急救、護理、醫療專業等意思，而且它亦不應作為商業目的，比如用於廣告或產品之中。 <br />\n<br />\n雖然紅十字會的說法聽起來好像合情合理，但 Introversion 卻對此感到相當婉惜，皆因紅十字會在執行這條規則時並不一致，現時很多遊戲、電影及電視節目都有採用這個符號，但卻偏偏只有他們這款獨立遊戲被盯上，並表示此舉在技術上已違反日內瓦公約及英國法例。不論如何，Introversion 目前已經透過更新刪除遊戲中的紅色十字，而且有部份遊戲原來亦一早作出變更，比如近年《Halo》系列已將急救包上的紅色十字改為紅色 H 字，而 H 就等於 Health 這個意思。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://js1.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/002-61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjs1.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F002-61.jpg&h=c69e8c46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"185e5f79d9acb6af67b28a9f4ceb141c51f43b96","tid":86767,"uid":7190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T13:39:38.000Z","msg":"咁把炮 叫埋英格蘭 格魯吉亞改旗囉"},{"pid":"0fb0c1408139352bc52a66366dba9d73d36d877d","tid":86767,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T13:47:36.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2b1d85b14a2bd13782941ddc3ba89bf692631b","tid":86767,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T13:51:52.000Z","msg":"ot<br />\n<br />\n唔捐血行動需要你支持<br />\n<br />\n私院免費取血，比邊個用大家心照<br />\n<br />\n97 後個個月告急，點解，心照"},{"pid":"a0d7e5db4918693c5ebf874b4fbf08dd34570a24","tid":86767,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T13:53:09.000Z","msg":"以後唔捐血囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc6d07aa6dcd0c211755947e95aa0544de7b37e","tid":86767,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T13:53:41.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75a15d7cfb4f4118090c4de424ef52186b66d2b","tid":86767,"uid":56444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T13:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d3a9977d7909a157c3f84eb189bb6da836b5f3","tid":86767,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:00:50.000Z","msg":"紅十字做乜咁似中國人玻璃心??"},{"pid":"8b6312c357ee9aa86af7ab12c0288a754c241de7","tid":86767,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:39:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁把炮 叫埋英格蘭 格魯吉亞改旗囉</blockquote><br />\nshutupmedpack.jpg"},{"pid":"c5c1354daf2f658b6837cd125305a7b8e5f3c266","tid":86767,"uid":19353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:44:51.000Z","msg":"肯定係紅十字條友買左隻game唔好玩 做鳩佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff53ddc9ffd8e543c452ddc